I don't believe it's appropriate of you

15
00:00:59,466 --> 00:01:00,600
to call my fiance at this hour.

16
00:01:00,600 --> 00:01:01,620
Brother Yun Su.

17
00:01:01,620 --> 00:01:03,066
I'm not your brother.

18
00:01:03,700 --> 00:01:04,700
I'm your elder.

19
00:01:05,166 --> 00:01:06,766
You should call me uncle.

20
00:01:07,566 --> 00:01:09,533
Never contact her again.

21
00:01:10,620 --> 00:01:11,700
Block him.

22
00:01:13,460 --> 00:01:15,933
What do you have against Mufeng?

23
00:01:17,820 --> 00:01:18,900
Mufeng?

24
00:01:20,140 --> 00:01:22,133
The Wang father and son
are not as simple as they appear to be.

25
00:01:22,140 --> 00:01:23,566
What did he say?

26
00:01:24,020 --> 00:01:26,300
He said he wanted to see me tomorrow.

27
00:01:27,020 --> 00:01:28,766
He wants to see you?

28
00:01:30,540 --> 00:01:31,740
Fine.

29
00:01:31,740 --> 00:01:33,233
I'd like to see him too.

30
00:01:33,233 --> 00:01:34,066
Tell him

31
00:01:34,200 --> 00:01:35,200
to bring his father along.

32
00:01:35,200 --> 00:01:36,980
The four of us will meet.

33
